{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I have a studio in Berlin --"},{"time":3000,"text":"let me cue on here --"},{"time":5000,"text":"which is down there in this snow, just last weekend."},{"time":9000,"text":"In the studio we do a lot of experiments."},{"time":11000,"text":"I would consider the studio more like a laboratory."},{"time":13000,"text":"I have occasional meetings with scientists."},{"time":16000,"text":"And I have an academy, a part of the University of Fine Arts in Berlin."},{"time":20000,"text":"We have an annual gathering of people,"},{"time":22000,"text":"and that is called Life in Space."},{"time":24000,"text":"Life in Space is really not necessarily about"},{"time":28000,"text":"how we do things, but why we do things."}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"Do you mind looking, with me, at that little cross in the center there?"},{"time":35000,"text":"So just keep looking. Don't mind me."},{"time":38000,"text":"So you will have a yellow circle, and we will do an after-image experiment."},{"time":42000,"text":"When the circle goes away you will have another color, the complementary color."},{"time":47000,"text":"I am saying something. And your eyes and your brain are saying something back."},{"time":51000,"text":"This whole idea of sharing, the idea of constituting reality"},{"time":54000,"text":"by overlapping what I say and what you say --"},{"time":58000,"text":"think of a movie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":60000,"text":"Since two years now, with some stipends from the science ministry in Berlin,"},{"time":63000,"text":"I've been working on these films"},{"time":67000,"text":"where we produce the film together."},{"time":70000,"text":"I don't necessarily think the film is so interesting."},{"time":72000,"text":"Obviously this is not interesting at all in the sense of the narrative."},{"time":75000,"text":"But nevertheless, what the potential is --"},{"time":77000,"text":"and just keep looking there --"},{"time":79000,"text":"what the potential is, obviously,"},{"time":81000,"text":"is to kind of move the border of who is the author,"},{"time":83000,"text":"and who is the receiver."},{"time":85000,"text":"Who is the consumer, if you want,"},{"time":88000,"text":"and who has responsibility for what one sees?"},{"time":91000,"text":"I think there is a socializing dimension"},{"time":94000,"text":"in, kind of, moving that border."},{"time":97000,"text":"Who decides what reality is?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":99000,"text":"This is the Tate Modern in London."},{"time":101000,"text":"The show was, in a sense, about that."},{"time":104000,"text":"It was about a space in which I put half a semi-circular yellow disk."},{"time":109000,"text":"I also put a mirror in the ceiling, and some fog, some haze."},{"time":112000,"text":"And my idea was to make the space tangible."},{"time":115000,"text":"With such a big space, the problem is"},{"time":117000,"text":"obviously that there is a discrepancy"},{"time":119000,"text":"between what your body can embrace,"},{"time":121000,"text":"and what the space, in that sense, is."},{"time":123000,"text":"So here I had the hope that by inserting some natural elements,"},{"time":127000,"text":"if you want -- some fog -- I could make the space tangible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130000,"text":"And what happens is that people, they start to see themselves in this space."},{"time":133000,"text":"So look at this. Look at the girl."},{"time":135000,"text":"Of course they have to look through a bloody camera"},{"time":137000,"text":"in a museum. Right? That's how museums are working today."},{"time":140000,"text":"But look at her face there,"},{"time":142000,"text":"as she's checking out, looking at herself in the mirror."},{"time":144000,"text":"\"Oh! That was my foot there!\""},{"time":146000,"text":"She wasn't really sure whether she was seeing herself or not."},{"time":149000,"text":"And in that whole idea,"},{"time":153000,"text":"how do we configure the relationship between our body and the space?"},{"time":157000,"text":"How do we reconfigure it?"},{"time":159000,"text":"How do we know that being in a space makes a difference?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162000,"text":"Do you see when I said in the beginning, it's about"},{"time":165000,"text":"why, rather than how?"},{"time":167000,"text":"The why meant really,"},{"time":169000,"text":"\"What consequences does it have when I take a step?\""},{"time":172000,"text":"\"What does it matter?\""},{"time":174000,"text":"\"Does it matter if I am in the world or not?\""},{"time":177000,"text":"\"And does it matter whether the kind of actions I take"},{"time":180000,"text":"filter into a sense of responsibility?\""},{"time":183000,"text":"Is art about that?"},{"time":185000,"text":"I would say yes. It is obviously about"},{"time":187000,"text":"not just about decorating the world, and making it look even better,"},{"time":190000,"text":"or even worse, if you ask me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":192000,"text":"It's obviously also about taking responsibility,"},{"time":195000,"text":"like I did here when throwing some green dye in the river"},{"time":197000,"text":"in L.A., Stockholm, Norway and Tokyo,"},{"time":201000,"text":"among other places."},{"time":203000,"text":"The green dye is not environmentally dangerous,"},{"time":205000,"text":"but it obviously looks really rather frightening."},{"time":207000,"text":"And it's on the other side also, I think, quite beautiful,"},{"time":211000,"text":"as it somehow shows the turbulence in these kind of downtown areas,"},{"time":216000,"text":"in these different places of the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"The \"Green river,\" as a kind of activist idea, not a part of an exhibition,"},{"time":222000,"text":"it was really about showing people,"},{"time":225000,"text":"in this city, as they walk by,"},{"time":228000,"text":"that space has dimensions. A space has time."},{"time":233000,"text":"And the water flows through the city with time."},{"time":236000,"text":"The water has an ability to make"},{"time":238000,"text":"the city negotiable, tangible."},{"time":240000,"text":"Negotiable meaning that it makes a difference"},{"time":242000,"text":"whether you do something or not."},{"time":244000,"text":"It makes a difference whether you say, \"I'm a part of this city."},{"time":246000,"text":"And if I vote it makes a difference."},{"time":248000,"text":"If I take a stand, it makes a difference.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":250000,"text":"This whole idea of a city not being a picture is,"},{"time":254000,"text":"I think, something that art, in a sense,"},{"time":256000,"text":"always was working with."},{"time":258000,"text":"The idea that art can actually evaluate the relationship"},{"time":261000,"text":"between what it means to be in a picture,"},{"time":266000,"text":"and what it means to be in a space. What is the difference?"},{"time":268000,"text":"The difference between thinking and doing."},{"time":271000,"text":"So these are different experiments with that. I won't go into them."},{"time":274000,"text":"Iceland, lower right corner, my favorite place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"These kinds of experiments, they filter into architectural models."},{"time":283000,"text":"These are ongoing experiments."},{"time":286000,"text":"One is an experiment I did for BMW,"},{"time":289000,"text":"an attempt to make a car."},{"time":291000,"text":"It's made out of ice."},{"time":293000,"text":"A crystalline stackable principle in the center on the top,"},{"time":296000,"text":"which I am trying to turn into a concert hall in Iceland."},{"time":299000,"text":"A sort of a run track, or a walk track,"},{"time":302000,"text":"on the top of a museum in Denmark,"},{"time":304000,"text":"which is made of colored glass, going all around."},{"time":308000,"text":"So the movement with your legs"},{"time":310000,"text":"will change the color of your horizon."},{"time":312000,"text":"And two summers ago at the Hyde Park in London,"},{"time":314000,"text":"with the Serpentine Gallery:"},{"time":316000,"text":"a kind of a temporal pavilion where"},{"time":318000,"text":"moving was the only way you could see the pavilion."},{"time":322000,"text":"This summer, in New York:"},{"time":324000,"text":"there is one thing about falling water which is very much about"},{"time":326000,"text":"the time it takes for water to fall."},{"time":328000,"text":"It's quite simple and fundamental."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331000,"text":"I've walked a lot in the mountains in Iceland."},{"time":333000,"text":"And as you come to a new valley,"},{"time":335000,"text":"as you come to a new landscape, you have a certain view."},{"time":337000,"text":"If you stand still, the landscape"},{"time":339000,"text":"doesn't necessarily tell you how big it is."},{"time":343000,"text":"It doesn't really tell you what you're looking at."},{"time":346000,"text":"The moment you start to move, the mountain starts to move."},{"time":349000,"text":"The big mountains far away, they move less."},{"time":351000,"text":"The small mountains in the foreground, they move more."},{"time":353000,"text":"And if you stop again, you wonder,"},{"time":355000,"text":"\"Is that a one-hour valley?"},{"time":357000,"text":"Or is that a three-hour hike, or is that a whole day I'm looking at?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":360000,"text":"If you have a waterfall in there,"},{"time":362000,"text":"right out there at the horizon; you look at the waterfall"},{"time":364000,"text":"and you go, \"Oh, the water is falling really slowly.\""},{"time":368000,"text":"And you go, \"My god it's really far away and it's a giant waterfall.\""},{"time":371000,"text":"If a waterfall is falling faster,"},{"time":374000,"text":"it's a smaller waterfall which is closer by --"},{"time":377000,"text":"because the speed of falling water is pretty constant everywhere."},{"time":381000,"text":"And your body somehow knows that."},{"time":384000,"text":"So this means a waterfall is a way of measuring space."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388000,"text":"Of course being an iconic city like New York,"},{"time":392000,"text":"that has had an interest in somehow"},{"time":394000,"text":"playing around with the sense of space, you could say that New York"},{"time":397000,"text":"wants to seem as big as possible."},{"time":399000,"text":"Adding a measurement"},{"time":401000,"text":"to that is interesting:"},{"time":403000,"text":"the falling water suddenly gives you a sense"},{"time":405000,"text":"of, \"Oh, Brooklyn is exactly this much --"},{"time":407000,"text":"the distance between Brooklyn and Manhattan, in this case"},{"time":410000,"text":"the lower East River is this big.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":413000,"text":"So it was not just necessarily about putting nature into the cities."},{"time":416000,"text":"It was also about giving the city a sense of dimension."},{"time":418000,"text":"And why would we want to do that?"},{"time":420000,"text":"Because I think it makes a difference"},{"time":422000,"text":"whether you have a body"},{"time":425000,"text":"that feels a part of a space,"},{"time":427000,"text":"rather than having a body which is just in front of a picture."},{"time":429000,"text":"And \"Ha-ha, there is a picture and here is I. And what does it matter?\""},{"time":432000,"text":"Is there a sense of consequences?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"So if I have a sense of the space,"},{"time":437000,"text":"if I feel that the space is tangible,"},{"time":439000,"text":"if I feel there is time,"},{"time":441000,"text":"if there is a dimension I could call time,"},{"time":443000,"text":"I also feel that I can change the space."},{"time":445000,"text":"And suddenly it makes a difference"},{"time":447000,"text":"in terms of making space accessible."},{"time":450000,"text":"One could say this is about"},{"time":452000,"text":"community, collectivity."},{"time":454000,"text":"It's about being together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456000,"text":"How do we create public space?"},{"time":459000,"text":"What does the word \"public\" mean today anyway?"},{"time":461000,"text":"So, asked in that way,"},{"time":463000,"text":"I think it raises great things about"},{"time":465000,"text":"parliamentary ideas, democracy, public space,"},{"time":468000,"text":"being together, being individual."},{"time":470000,"text":"How do we create"},{"time":473000,"text":"an idea which is both tolerant to individuality,"},{"time":476000,"text":"and also to collectivity,"},{"time":478000,"text":"without polarizing the two"},{"time":480000,"text":"into two different opposites?"},{"time":483000,"text":"Of course the political agendas in the world"},{"time":486000,"text":"has been very obsessed, polarizing the two against each other"},{"time":489000,"text":"into different, very normative ideas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"I would claim that art and culture,"},{"time":493000,"text":"and this is why art and culture are so incredibly interesting"},{"time":496000,"text":"in the times we're living in now,"},{"time":498000,"text":"have proven that one can"},{"time":500000,"text":"create a kind of a space"},{"time":503000,"text":"which is both sensitive to individuality"},{"time":505000,"text":"and to collectivity."},{"time":507000,"text":"It's very much about this causality, consequences."},{"time":510000,"text":"It's very much about the way we link"},{"time":514000,"text":"thinking and doing."},{"time":516000,"text":"So what is between thinking and doing?"},{"time":518000,"text":"And right in-between thinking and doing,"},{"time":520000,"text":"I would say, there is experience."},{"time":522000,"text":"And experience is not just"},{"time":524000,"text":"a kind of entertainment in a non-casual way."},{"time":527000,"text":"Experience is about responsibility."},{"time":529000,"text":"Having an experience is taking part in the world."},{"time":533000,"text":"Taking part in the world is really about sharing responsibility."},{"time":537000,"text":"So art, in that sense,"},{"time":539000,"text":"I think holds an incredible relevance"},{"time":542000,"text":"in the world in which we're moving into,"},{"time":545000,"text":"particularly right now."},{"time":547000,"text":"That's all I have. Thank you very much."},{"time":549000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}